rows.label: tlk41300011_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Yo, Rex.
Looks like salvaging is going pretty well for you.

rows.label: tlk41300011_01_msg0001
rows.name: Have you been to the Central Exchange?

rows.label: tlk41300011_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You should take the stuff you salvage there,
be it collection items or treasure.

rows.label: tlk41300011_01_msg0003
rows.name:
If you can get them to buy it as a set,
you can sell it for more than if you sold it
individually.

rows.label: tlk41300011_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Making good use of that is what makes
a fine salvager.
